featureType.title: ADMIN USE ONLY - reduced (5,000m) version of current NBHL
featureType.abstract:
This layer is created from an SQL Server view of the NBHL - a product of SELECT geom.Reduce(5000)
This layer exists exclusively for seeding problematic zoom levels too avoid GC overhead limit issues and Geoserver crashing. Currently, it is not used in a zoom-based layer group, but could be incorporated at levels 8 or less.
